title: Can Minnesota Pop?
description:
Bill Barnwell joins Mina to discuss the trades that were and weren't made at the deadline. Then they preview the best games of the Week 9 slate including Rams-Bucs, Vikings-Commanders, Chargers-Falcons, Titans-Chiefs, and more.
